1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,539
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,539 --> 00:01:37,979
Episode 4

3
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:40,340
Did we invite Mr. Chang and Mrs. Chang?

4
00:01:40,630 --> 00:01:41,229
Yes.

5
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,340
My goodness.

6
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:46,259
The…

7
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,380
Come again if it’s not enough.

8
00:01:49,460 --> 00:01:50,100
It’s enough.

9
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:50,820
Thank you.

10
00:01:52,340 --> 00:01:53,580
Look.

11
00:01:53,770 --> 00:01:55,020
After changing your clothes,

12
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,460
you look so pretty.

13
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:05,820
Gosh. Damn it.

14
00:02:05,820 --> 00:02:06,500
Send it quickly.

15
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:06,980
Okay.

16
00:02:07,420 --> 00:02:08,860
What can I do?

17
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:10,970
Come with me.

18
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:22,680
Xiang’er.

19
00:02:23,470 --> 00:02:25,440
What’s the matter you can tell me
in front of Guixiu?

20
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:26,980
It seems to be mysterious.

21
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:28,130
What’s wrong with you?

22
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:31,420
You knew Chang Zhixin and Jiang Mengping
would come,

23
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,140
why did you invite Shang Xirui here to perform?

24
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:34,200
Are they coming?

25
00:02:37,820 --> 00:02:38,780
It doesn’t matter.

26
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:41,610
It’ll be noisy today.

27
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,500
They may not get recognized even face to face.

28
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:44,530
Besides,

29
00:02:44,940 --> 00:02:45,690
