30
00:02:46,170 --> 00:02:47,400
Jiang Mengping is married.

31
00:02:47,670 --> 00:02:49,600
It’s all in the past.

32
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:53,140
You know Shang Xirui’s temper, don’t you?

33
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:54,540
He’s a bit sensitive.

34
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:56,180
He’s as nutty as a fruitcake, you know?

35
00:02:56,180 --> 00:02:57,510
Don’t worry.

36
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,200
I’m here today.

37
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:00,670
He dares not.

38
00:03:01,230 --> 00:03:01,790
Come.

39
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:04,500
Sit down.

40
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:06,740
Forget it.

41
00:03:06,740 --> 00:03:07,670
It’s hard to say it clearly.

42
00:03:09,270 --> 00:03:09,820
Mr. Han.

43
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,210
Come over here.

44
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,329
Mrs. Cao.

45
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,650
Call a carriage, quickly.

46
00:03:17,870 --> 00:03:19,230
Send Mr. Chang and Mrs. Chang back.

47
00:03:19,230 --> 00:03:20,380
Tell them they have some relatives home.

48
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,420
Where are the relatives from?

49
00:03:24,530 --> 00:03:25,790
Pingyang of course.

50
00:03:26,150 --> 00:03:27,260
Go. Quickly.

51
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:28,240
I will explain it to you later.

52
00:03:28,420 --> 00:03:29,230
Hurry.

53
00:03:29,850 --> 00:03:30,350
Okay.

54
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:32,970
Xiang’er. You…

55
00:03:33,530 --> 00:03:35,020
You are making a fuss.

56
00:03:35,140 --> 00:03:35,950
Is it that serious?

57
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:37,380
Of course it is.

58
00:03:38,740 --> 00:03:40,040
Why don’t you get it?

59
00:03:41,050 --> 00:03:42,060
I’ll die from worry.

60
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:42,940
My goodness.

61
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:51,430
Chopsticks.

62
00:03:51,890 --> 00:03:52,510
Chopsticks.

63
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:53,960
Here you are.

64
00:03:59,590 --> 00:04:00,540
You silly girl.

65
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:03,600
You’ve met some big shots with me.

66
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:06,070
The Cheng’s Mansion used to be
a palace of a prince.

67
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:08,260
But it’s not a prince who lives in it now.

68
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:09,740
What are you afraid of?

69
00:04:10,510 --> 00:04:10,820
I…

70
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:12,230
I’m not.

71
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:18,870
Leader.

72
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:21,060
How about we don’t

73
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,180
keep performing today?

74
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:26,950
Why not?

75
00:04:27,620 --> 00:04:28,350
Leader.

76
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:29,550
Leader.

77
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:31,140
Commander Cao’s wife

78
00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:32,950
