79
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:35,560
Are you afraid of her?

80
00:04:36,740 --> 00:04:38,260
-I.
-She is not that frightening.

81
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:39,620
Anyhow, she

82
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:41,120
may come here to ask us to leave.

83
00:04:41,450 --> 00:04:42,070
What should we do?

84
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:45,060
I even don’t want to deal with her.

85
00:04:45,540 --> 00:04:46,340
Try to help me stop her.

86
00:04:46,340 --> 00:04:47,020
I will perform first.

87
00:04:47,380 --> 00:04:47,720
No.

88
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,380
Leader.

89
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:51,450
Who are the one come for us from Pingyang?

90
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,380
Are they your family?

91
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,290
I’m a bit afraid.

92
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:54,820
Don’t be afraid.

93
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:55,860
You think

94
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:57,620
