95
00:04:58,380 --> 00:04:59,380
Zhixin, Mengping.

96
00:05:00,150 --> 00:05:00,710
Where are you going?

97
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,150
It’ll begin very soon.

98
00:05:02,580 --> 00:05:04,220
Mr. Han said some relatives from Pingyang came.

99
00:05:04,220 --> 00:05:05,040
We will go back now.

100
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:06,410
Yes.

101
00:05:07,010 --> 00:05:08,120
What?

102
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,770
Who will come at this moment?

103
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,320
How about this?

104
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,710
You take your seats now.

105
00:05:13,460 --> 00:05:14,860
Later I will ask a car

106
00:05:14,860 --> 00:05:15,560
to pick them up.

107
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:16,070
Is it okay?

108
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:18,020
It’s been a good day. Let’s get in and enjoy.

109
00:05:18,530 --> 00:05:19,620
-Come on.
-It’s inappropriate.

110
00:05:19,650 --> 00:05:20,360
Right, Mr. Han.

111
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:22,540
Arrange a car to pick them up.

112
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:23,400
Let’s go.

113
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:24,940
Come.

114
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:26,530
You’d let us get back.

115
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:28,140
We can’t just let them there.

116
00:05:28,140 --> 00:05:29,380
-Right?
-Come on. Let’s enjoy.

117
00:05:29,580 --> 00:05:30,460
It’s inappropriate.

118
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:31,920
Just let us go. Pick them up.

119
00:05:32,659 --> 00:05:33,700
Sit down.

120
00:05:35,030 --> 00:05:35,470
It begins.

121
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:48,290
On the first birthday ceremony of Young Master,

122
00:05:49,020 --> 00:05:52,690
Shuiyun Theater wishes Young Master good fortune,

123
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:54,200
long life, health and peace.

124
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:55,930
Great.

125
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,620
At the request of the Master,

126
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:03,500
I will show you distinguished guests

127
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:06,500
a Shanxi opera, Bao Zheng Apologizes.

128
00:06:06,970 --> 00:06:07,790
For any part not good enough,

129
00:06:08,110 --> 00:06:09,420
please excuse me.

130
00:06:09,770 --> 00:06:12,380
Mr. Shang can play a versed role today.

131
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:14,160
Great.

132
00:06:15,260 --> 00:06:15,900
Great.

133
00:06:30,210 --> 00:06:31,180
Miss. Jiang. Where are you going?

134
00:06:32,450 --> 00:06:33,390
It’s none of your business.

135
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:38,140
Are you going to leave with Chang Zhixin?

136
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,500
He’s not a good guy.

137
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:42,250
It’ll have no good for you to be with him.

138
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,420
You only met him a few times.

139
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:44,430
You can’t say him like that.

140
00:06:45,780 --> 00:06:47,700
You are not the first one from Shuiyun Theater

141
00:06:47,700 --> 00:06:48,650
