142
00:06:48,909 --> 00:06:50,300
Do you think the others have a good marriage?

143
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:51,200
But Chang Zhixin is different.

144
00:06:52,980 --> 00:06:55,420
All childes of the rich families are the same.

145
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,920
Even if I finally

146
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,310
