147
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:00,190
I won’t blame on him.

148
00:07:00,660 --> 00:07:01,560
It’s my choice.

149
00:07:03,090 --> 00:07:03,580
If…

150
00:07:03,930 --> 00:07:04,740
If you leave,

151
00:07:04,740 --> 00:07:05,930
