152
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,020
Give it up.

153
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,720
We’ve agreed we will have a new opera every year.

154
00:07:11,260 --> 00:07:12,870
Now we just have it started.

155
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:13,740
So will you leave me here alone?

156
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:19,020
It’s just a joke for our young.

157
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:21,340
You don’t need to take it seriously.

158
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:23,370
I’m serious about every single word you’ve said.

159
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:25,800
Take it as I let you down.

160
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,000
Miss. Jiang. Miss. Jiang.

161
00:07:29,450 --> 00:07:30,580
Miss. Jiang. You can’t lie to me.

162
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:30,970
Miss. Jiang.

163
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:31,710
Miss. Jiang.

164
00:07:31,820 --> 00:07:33,220
We’ve reached an agreement.

165
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:33,520
Let go of me.

166
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:35,020
Miss. Jiang.

167
00:07:36,700 --> 00:07:37,440
Jiang Mengping

168
00:07:40,420 --> 00:07:42,170
If you leave today,

169
00:07:43,250 --> 00:07:45,140
we are no longer friends.

170
00:07:46,610 --> 00:07:49,390
We’ll be enemies when we meet next time.

171
