Fine. Alright.

209
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:48,700
We are of the same family.

210
00:09:49,710 --> 00:09:51,600
-Don’t make it unpleasant.
-Yes.

211
00:09:51,700 --> 00:09:53,000
Sit down. Guixiu, please sit down.

212
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:54,920
-Sit down and listen to the opera.
-Commander.

213
00:09:55,260 --> 00:09:56,140
Listen to the opera.

214
