272
00:12:50,380 --> 00:12:52,130
even if many years have passed.

273
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:54,360
What a bad fate!

274
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:56,040
Shut up.

275
00:12:56,980 --> 00:12:58,370
You are the one to blame.

276
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:00,660
We almost could avoid it.

277
00:13:00,900 --> 00:13:02,250
But you asked them back.

278
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:04,140
You haven’t done something good

279
00:13:04,140 --> 00:13:05,670
but always creating troubles.

280
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:06,460
What?

281
00:13:06,460 --> 00:13:07,660
